BuildGoal
/ Builds a single goal - two LLM passes:
/ Pass 1: Module selection (sees entire goal for context)
/ Pass 2: Step building (per step, parallelized)

- [plang] GetRuntime2Goal %goal%, write to %r2Goal%
- write out "Building goal: %r2Goal.Name%"
- read file "llm/SelectActions.llm", load vars, write to %selectActionsPrompt%
- [llm] system: %selectActionsPrompt%
        user: %r2Goal%
        scheme: [{stepIndex: int, action: string, intent: string}]
        write to %actionAssignments%
- write out "Action assignments: %actionAssignments%"
- foreach %actionAssignments%, call AssignAction, item=%assignment%, r2Goal=%r2Goal%
- write out "Steps count: %r2Goal.Steps.Count%"
- foreach %r2Goal.Steps%, call BuildStep, item=%step%
- [plang] call SaveGoal with Runtime2.Core.Goal %r2Goal%
